<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello Richard &amp; A=
ll,</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I appreciate the res=
ponse. We will complete the testing on Friday afternoon, as described below,=
 and provide the laboratory results along with the corresponding reports as s=
oon as we have them back.
</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">It would assist us i=
n completing the tests with efficiency if we could have maximum insight, by h=
aving the following questions from my previous email answered prior:</span><=
o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">To ensure effectu=
al testing it would be beneficial if you could confirm the following:</span>=
</u><o:p></o:p></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0in" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 l=
fo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">That the chlorine was located in the l=
aundry room downstairs at the time of the fire.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li cl=
ass=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><=
span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The quantity of the chlorine that was in tha=
t room at the time of the fire. 1 container ?</span><o:p></o:p></li><li clas=
s=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><sp=
an style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Where there any
<u>other chemicals</u> that were located in that same room, or anywhere else=
 downstairs. &nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</=
span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many Thanks,</span><=
o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant.</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
