<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;=
Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">From:</span></b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;fo=
nt-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"> Raffaella del Prete &lt;<a href=3D=
"mailto:raffaellanz@icloud.com">raffaellanz@icloud.com</a>&gt;
<br>
<b>Sent:</b> Friday, October 10, 2025 4:53 PM<br>
<b>To:</b> Grant Metson &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Gran=
