r.co.nz">Bryan.Strong@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;;
 Kelly Mason &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Kelly.Mason@tower.co.nz">Kelly.Mason@towe=
r.co.nz</a>&gt;; Chris Cornwall &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Chris.Cornwall@tower.c=
o.nz">Chris.Cornwall@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;; Megan Jensen &lt;<a href=3D"mailto=
:Megan.Jensen@tower.co.nz">Megan.Jensen@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: C90306048 - Fire at 23 Mays Street, Devonport [WW-ACTIVE=
.FID3167762]</span><o:p></o:p></p>
